      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Union men in Tacoma are open\ning a fight on Judge Smell. who re-\nGently announced his candidacy for\nthe U. S. senate. 1t is charged\nthat Judge Smell let contract to\nan open shop contractor and is en-\nploying nonunion labor at the pres\nent time. The open shop fight has\nbeen the leading labor issue in the\nTacoma building trades for some\ntime and it is likely that an ener-\ngetic fight will be made against\nJudge Smell by organized labor\nthere in consequence."
    }
